Class Vip

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.User
      • entities.Vip
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Vip
extends User
    Features of VIP users: 1. They can select a event and put it in their Interested Events, which works as a wishlist 2. They can "follow" their favourite speakers and get notified when there are new events schedules with their favourite speakers 3. They can hold a party
